  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Features】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A casual game with roguelike elements where you fight alongside your fellows, decorated with style of a picture scroll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【How to clear?】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and destroy all the torii gates to survive the \"Hyakki Yako\"!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies to collect orbs and enhance yourself and your fellows before taking on the challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/2fe657f94d55dda80a99eb29225d69be.poster.avif?t=1738915306\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/2fe657f94d55dda80a99eb29225d69be.webm?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/2fe657f94d55dda80a99eb29225d69be.mp4?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Switching attack methods】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left-click on the mouse or press the A button on a gamepad to switch between distribute and concentrate attacks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use it according to the situation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/9005fe361caba75f9cc15b52b0ea1600.poster.avif?t=1738915306\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/9005fe361caba75f9cc15b52b0ea1600.webm?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/9005fe361caba75f9cc15b52b0ea1600.mp4?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Place your fellows】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take advantage of your fellows characteristics when arranging them to create the strongest formation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/014f2cf3dedb24f5c3d522ffb11f8c41.poster.avif?t=1738915306\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/014f2cf3dedb24f5c3d522ffb11f8c41.webm?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/014f2cf3dedb24f5c3d522ffb11f8c41.mp4?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【A wide variety of fierce warriors】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's make good use of distinctive characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/c64d8f8f8208d22ea72aee5df02149e2.poster.avif?t=1738915306\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/c64d8f8f8208d22ea72aee5df02149e2.webm?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/c64d8f8f8208d22ea72aee5df02149e2.mp4?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Features】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A casual game with roguelike elements where you fight alongside your fellows, decorated with style of a picture scroll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【How to clear?】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and destroy all the torii gates to survive the \"Hyakki Yako\"!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies to collect orbs and enhance yourself and your fellows before taking on the challenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/2fe657f94d55dda80a99eb29225d69be.poster.avif?t=1738915306\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/2fe657f94d55dda80a99eb29225d69be.webm?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/2fe657f94d55dda80a99eb29225d69be.mp4?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Switching attack methods】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left-click on the mouse or press the A button on a gamepad to switch between distribute and concentrate attacks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use it according to the situation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/9005fe361caba75f9cc15b52b0ea1600.poster.avif?t=1738915306\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/9005fe361caba75f9cc15b52b0ea1600.webm?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/9005fe361caba75f9cc15b52b0ea1600.mp4?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【Place your fellows】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take advantage of your fellows characteristics when arranging them to create the strongest formation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/014f2cf3dedb24f5c3d522ffb11f8c41.poster.avif?t=1738915306\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/014f2cf3dedb24f5c3d522ffb11f8c41.webm?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/014f2cf3dedb24f5c3d522ffb11f8c41.mp4?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【A wide variety of fierce warriors】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let's make good use of distinctive characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/c64d8f8f8208d22ea72aee5df02149e2.poster.avif?t=1738915306\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/c64d8f8f8208d22ea72aee5df02149e2.webm?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2910990/extras/c64d8f8f8208d22ea72aee5df02149e2.mp4?t=1738915306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
